      <title>如何在手机上使用git</title>
      <link href="2020/10/21/%E8%AE%BA%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%A8%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8git/"/>
      <url>2020/10/21/%E8%AE%BA%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%A8%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8git/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>准备工具:安卓手机一台(安卓7.0以上)，utermux</strong></p><p><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1nWqcYv8Htfojos21fmIrzw#/multshare/%2FUTermux%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%2F/%2FTermux_%E8%87%AA%E7%94%A8%E5%8C%85%2F%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95%E5%8C%85">ut链接，提取码mjvu</a></p><p>打开ut,执行以下命令:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$  pkg install git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>有y/n这种提示直接选y就可以。</p><p>安装完之后使用git –version检测一下。</p><p>现在应该可以用git clone了，但是你可能想用手机ssh连接gitee,github和gitlab。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> $  ssh-keygen -t rsa -C youremail@youremail.com</span><br><span class="line"># 上面的命令要是生成失败就用atilo安装个debian再在debian里生成。三次回车即可生成。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>执行命令cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub查看公匙。</p><p>然后注册gitee,github和gitlab账号，把公匙在设置里面添加一下。</p><p><strong>gitee,github和gitlab可以用一个公匙。</strong></p><p>添加后，在终端输入:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> #Gitee</span><br><span class="line"> $ ssh -T git@gitee.com</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#GitHub</span><br><span class="line"> $ ssh -T git@github.com</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#Gitlab</span><br><span class="line"> $ ssh -T git@gitlab.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再次执行上面的命令，检查是否成功连接，如果返回以下信息，则表示添加成功:You’ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.(github的,gitee也差不多，但是gitlab的不太一样)</p><p> 接下来我们要设置一些信息</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git config --global user.name &quot;yourname&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$ git config --global user.email &quot;youremail@youremail.com&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>name尽量和码云或GitHub保持一致，但email必须是码云或GitHub注册时使用的邮箱。命令不分前后，没有顺序。</strong></p><p>git使用教程自己找吧，比如<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/yiven/p/8465054.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/yiven/p/8465054.html</a>。</p><p><strong>END</strong></p>]]></content>
      
      
